            <time class="sm:w-28 text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">2017</time>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Event 1</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Aliquam vel cursus nisi, vestibulum dignissim tortor. Fusce blandit nec lorem at convallis. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
